BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (In the golden savanna of Africa, where the grass grew tall and the sun painted everything) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (amber, there lived a baby elephant named Kalu.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Kalu was the smallest elephant in his herd. His ears were too big, his trunk was too) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (short, and his legs were a little wobbly.) Tj ET
