BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (terrified of water.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (Every other elephant loved splashing in rivers and lakes. But not Kalu. Water made his) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (knees shake.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: A small baby elephant with oversized ears standing at the edge of the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (savanna, looking nervously at a distant river while other elephants play in the water) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (happily]) Tj ET
