BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 17) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td ('Anyone can do something when they're not afraid,' Big Tembo continued.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td ('But to do the right thing when every part of you is screaming with fear? When your legs) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (are shaking and your heart is pounding?') Tj ET
