stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 18) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (That night, Grandmother Elephant found Kalu and wrapped her trunk around him again.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td ('I'm so proud of you,' she whispered. 'You found out what to do with your fear.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td ('I'm still afraid of water, Grandma,' Kalu admitted. 'My legs still shake when I see the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (river.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td ('And that's perfectly okay,' she said. 'Being brave doesn't mean the fear goes away. It) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (means you don't let it stop you from doing what's right.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.4 Td ([Illustration: Grandmother Elephant and Kalu under a starry night sky, her trunk around) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td (him lovingly, a peaceful nighttime savanna scene]) Tj ET
endstream
