stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 20) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (And the most beautiful thing happened: the young elephants who used to tease him fell into) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (step beside him.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td ('We'll cross together,' they said. No more teasing. No more laughing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (Because they had learned something too   they learned that courage isn't about having no) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (fear.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (It's about having a heart big enough to act even when fear fills it up.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (And Kalu? Kalu had the biggest heart of all.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td ([Illustration: Kalu crossing the river surrounded by supportive young elephant friends on) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (all sides, all walking together through the water, a scene of solidarity and friendship]) Tj ET
endstream
