stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 21) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (From that day on, Kalu was known as the bravest elephant in the herd   not because he) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (stopped being afraid.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (He was still afraid of water. He was still afraid of thunder. He was still afraid of the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (dark.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (But whenever someone needed help, whenever something right needed to be done, Kalu was) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (always the first to step forward.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (Shaking legs and all.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td ([Illustration: Kalu grown slightly bigger, leading the herd confidently past a river,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (still with slightly nervous eyes but head held high, a hero among his people]) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
