stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 22) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (And whenever a young elephant came to him and said, 'Kalu, I'm too scared. I can't be) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (brave.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Kalu would wrap his trunk around them and say what his grandmother had taught him:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td ('Being brave doesn't mean you're not scared. Being brave means you do the right thing EVEN) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (when you're scared.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td ('So be scared. Shake and tremble and cry if you need to. But then take that step anyway.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td ('That's what courage really is. And you have more of it than you know.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td ([Illustration: Kalu as a young adult elephant, trunk wrapped around a small scared baby) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (elephant, giving wisdom and comfort under an acacia tree at sunset, a beautiful) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (passing-on-wisdom scene]) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
