BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 23) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (And here is what Kalu wants to whisper in YOUR ear, dear reader:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (You are braver than you believe. There will be rivers in your life   things that scare) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (you, things that seem impossible.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (Maybe it is the first day at a new school. Maybe it is standing up to a bully. Maybe it is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (trying something you have never done before.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (When that river comes, remember Kalu. Remember his shaking legs and pounding heart.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (And remember that he crossed anyway. Because courage is not the absence of fear. Courage) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.2 Td (is one step forward, even when you are terrified.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td ([Illustration: A child facing something scary in their own life   perhaps the first day of) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (school   with an imaginary Kalu standing behind them supportively, giving them strength]) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
55 0 obj
<< /Type /Page /Parent 2 0 R /MediaBox [0 0 612 792] /Contents 56 0 R /Resources << /Font << /F1 3 0 R /F2 4 0 R >> >> >>
endobj
56 0 obj
<< /Length 959 >>
stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 24) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (So when you feel scared, do not run from the feeling. Let it be there.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Say to yourself: 'I am scared. And that is okay. I am still going to try.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Because every brave person who ever lived was scared first. Every hero trembled before) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (they acted.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (The difference between a hero and everyone else is not that heroes feel no fear.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (It is that heroes feel the fear and move forward anyway. Just like Kalu. Just like you.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.4 Td ([Illustration: A powerful final image of Kalu silhouetted against a sunset, standing tall) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td (at a river crossing, water flowing beneath him, strong and brave, an inspiration for all) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (children facing their fears]) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
