stream
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 716.0 Td (Page 25) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.2 Td (What is YOUR river, dear reader? What is the thing that makes your knees shake and your) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.2 Td (heart pound?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.2 Td (Maybe it is speaking in front of your class. Maybe it is making new friends. Maybe it is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.2 Td (the dark, or heights, or trying something new.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.2 Td (Whatever your river is   know this: you can cross it. Not because the fear will go away.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.2 Td (But because YOU are brave enough to take that first step, even with shaking legs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.2 Td (Kalu believes in you. And so do I.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.4 Td ([Illustration: A child standing at the edge of their own 'river'   something scary they) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.4 Td (must face   with the spirit of brave Kalu standing supportively behind them, giving them) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td (courage]) Tj ET
endstream
