60 0 obj
<< /Length 687 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (The Moral of the Story) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Courage Isn't Being Fearless) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.4 Td (Kalu taught us that being brave doesn't mean you're never scared. Real courage means doing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.4 Td (the right thing even when you're terrified. Everyone is afraid of something   and that's) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.4 Td (okay! What matters is what you choose to do with your fear. You can let it freeze you in) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.4 Td (place, or you can take a deep breath, plant your feet, and step forward anyway. That's) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.4 Td (true bravery. And YOU are braver than you think.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
