62 0 obj
<< /Length 787 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Discussion Questions for Parents) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (After reading this story together, talk about these questions:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.4 Td (1. What is something that makes you feel scared? Is it okay to feel that way?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.6 Td (2. Can you think of a time when you did something even though you were afraid? How did it) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.6 Td (feel afterward?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.8 Td (3. Why do you think the other elephants stopped teasing Kalu after he saved Kofi?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 571.0 Td (4. What does Big Tembo mean when he says 'Courage is action in the presence of fear'?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 547.2 Td (5. How can you be brave for someone else, even when you feel scared inside?) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
