BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (Daniel Tesfamariam is a storyteller who believes every child deserves) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (stories that spark imagination, build character, and fill hearts with wonder.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.4 Td (His stories are crafted to help children understand important life lessons) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.4 Td (through adventure, friendship, and the magic of imagination.) Tj ET
